  "updated": 1775195186,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69cedaf81df132952631c816",
      "text": "ニュース要約サンプル 2026/04/03",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb5500000000008e1c58",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164246,
      "updated": 1775164246
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedaf900000000008e1c08",
      "text": "\trss feed3つほど指定してる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164211
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3300000000008e1c4e",
      "text": "\t以下powershell",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164211,
      "updated": 1775164216
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3f00000000008e1c56",
      "text": "\t\t$newsList にはrssから取ってきたデータが入る",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164224,
      "updated": 1775164234
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf1d39000000000099fdbd",
      "text": " \t\tニュースソースで指定しているの面白い、自分は検索ワードを指定している[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1775181114,
      "updated": 1775181136
    },
    {
      "id": "69cf542f00000000006d8e6d",
      "text": " \t\tなるほど[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775195185,
      "updated": 1775195186
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3700000000008e1c4f",
      "text": "\t\tcode:ps1",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164216,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3900000000008e1c50",
      "text": "\t\t $prompt = @\"",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164218,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3900000000008e1c51",
      "text": "   以下は今日のニュース見出し一覧です。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164218,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3900000000008e1c52",
      "text": "   カテゴリ別に分類し、日本語でわかりやすく要約してください。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164218,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3900000000008e1c53",
      "text": "   ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164218,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3900000000008e1c54",
      "text": "   $newsList",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164218,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb3900000000008e1c55",
      "text": "   \"@",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164218,
      "updated": 1775164218
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedb4c00000000008e1c57",
      "text": "  $prompt を claude に渡す",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164236,
      "updated": 1775164244
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedaf900000000008e1c09",
      "text": "code:md",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafa00000000008e1c0b",
      "text": " # デイリーニュース要約 - 2026-04-03",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c0c",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c0d",
      "text": " ## 2026年4月2日 ニュースまとめ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c0e",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c0f",
      "text": " ---",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c10",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c11",
      "text": " ### 国際情勢・戦争・政治",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c12",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c13",
      "text": " - **イラン戦争の影響が拡大** — 石油だけでなくヘリウム・アルミニウムの供給にも悪影響。iPhoneやAIインフラにも波及。イラン最大の製鉄所2か所もストライキで操業停止。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c14",
      "text": " - **マクロン仏大統領、トランプ氏のイラン対応を批判** — 「真剣に、毎日発言するな」と苦言。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c15",
      "text": " - **イランのノーベル賞受賞者が獄中で心臓発作の疑い** — 家族が報告。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c16",
      "text": " - **米国、ベネズエラ暫定指導者への制裁を解除** — デルシー・ロドリゲス氏が対象。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c17",
      "text": " - **EU、職員のAI生成画像使用を禁止** — AI画像を多用するトランプ大統領とは対照的な姿勢。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c18",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c19",
      "text": " ### セキュリティ・サイバー攻撃",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c1a",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c1b",
      "text": " - **北朝鮮ハッカー「UNC1069」がAxiosへのサプライチェーン攻撃の犯人** — Googleが特定。OSSライブラリを標的にした攻撃。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c1c",
      "text": " - **送金アプリDuc、免許証・パスポート数千件をネット上に公開状態で放置** — Amazonサーバーでのデータ漏洩。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c1d",
      "text": " - **ICEがParagonのスパイウェアを購入** — 麻薬密売捜査目的と説明。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c1e",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c1f",
      "text": " ### テクノロジー・AI",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c20",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c21",
      "text": " - **Microsoft、新たな基盤モデル3つを発表** — AI競争に本格参戦。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c22",
      "text": " - **ElevenLabs、AI音楽生成アプリをリリース** — 音声AI企業が音楽分野にも進出。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c23",
      "text": " - **Google Vidsアプリでプロンプトによるアバター操作が可能に**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c24",
      "text": " - **Claude Codeの内部構造を流出コードから解析した「Claude Code Unpacked」公開** — 未公開機能もソースから直接マッピング。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c25",
      "text": " - **OpenAI、ビジネストークショーTBPNを買収**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c26",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c27",
      "text": " ### ビジネス・経済",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c28",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c29",
      "text": " - **Oracle、最大3万人を解雇** — 事前通知なし、朝のメール1通で通告。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c2a",
      "text": " - **SpaceX、上場計画で企業価値1兆ドル規模に** — イーロン・マスク氏の宇宙企業。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c2b",
      "text": " - **Tesla、低価格車投入も販売減少に歯止めかからず**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c2c",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c2d",
      "text": " ### ハードウェア・ガジェット",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c2e",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c2f",
      "text": " - **Raspberry Pi、さらなる値上げを発表** — 旧モデルのRAM増量版も登場。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c30",
      "text": " - **NASA宇宙飛行士、宇宙からのメール送信に成功** — 「メール送信もロケットサイエンス」。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c31",
      "text": " - **Unitedアプリ、空港のTSA待ち時間を表示可能に**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c32",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c33",
      "text": " ### ソーシャルメディア・Web",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c34",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c35",
      "text": " - **Flipboardが「ソーシャルウェブサイト」機能を公開** — パブリッシャーやクリエイター向けにオープンなソーシャルウェブへの接続を支援。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c36",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c37",
      "text": " ### 事件・事故・災害",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c38",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c39",
      "text": " - **NYで乳母車の赤ちゃんが射殺される**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c3a",
      "text": " - **ウガンダの保育園で幼児4人が刺殺される**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c3b",
      "text": " - **アテネ付近の嵐で男性死亡** — クレタ島はサハラ砂塵に覆われる。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c3c",
      "text": " - **オランダで盗難された古代の黄金ヘルメット、1年以上を経て回収**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c3d",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c3e",
      "text": " ### 歴史・雑学",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c3f",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c40",
      "text": " - **世界初の飛行機死亡事故の犠牲者トーマス・セルフリッジ中尉** — その人物像を紹介。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c41",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c42",
      "text": " ### グルメ・キャンペーン",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c43",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c44",
      "text": " - **ハーゲンダッツ抹茶サンド「ザ・グリーンティー」レビュー** — 抹茶の渋味とアイスの甘味が好相性。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c45",
      "text": " - **GIGAZINE春のプレゼント大放出企画** — アンケート回答で全員プレゼント。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c46",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c47",
      "text": " ### その他",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c48",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c49",
      "text": " - **ブラジル、離婚時のペット共同親権を法制化**",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c4a",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
    {
      "id": "69cedafb00000000008e1c4b",
      "text": " ---",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1775164155,
      "updated": 1775164155
    },
